{"tid":525932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過濾再上枱！渝知名火鍋店「潲水油」做湯底","createTime":"2018-01-11T07:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T03:26:31.000Z","uid":23707,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"330634837203551c3967843415a6d642140db2d2","tid":525932,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180111/bkncn-20180111073052067-0111_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180111%2Fbkncn-20180111073052067-0111_05011_001.html&d=0j3e67mZ5s9ptsw%2B7DTk0DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d88c0e09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180111/bkncn-20180111073052067-0111_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"12f01ca994dfdee0a59fb8731721f9b5a40ce3d1","tid":525932,"uid":23707,"like":154,"dislike":0,"score":154,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180111/photo/bkncn-20180111073052067-0111_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180111153312\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180111%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180111073052067-0111_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180111153312&h=f835808a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地再爆有知名食肆使用食用後的餘渣材料，再上枱奉客醜聞！在全國16個省市擁有過百間門店，還被認定為重慶首批「放心火鍋店」的大隊長主題火鍋北城天街店，被揭發使用「口水油」做火鍋湯底。目前涉事火鍋店已被責令停業整頓。而事件被曝光，全因一名食客光顧過該火鍋店後肚痛不適，於是聘人到店內做「臥底」，終拍攝到店員用「口水油」作湯底的罪證。<br />\n<br />\n從網絡曝光涉事火鍋店廚房內部的短片所見，職員將收回的一鍋鍋顧客食完的湯底，用簡單工具隔住食物殘渣，將火鍋油倒入一個大鐵桶內，然後將殘渣倒進旁邊的大垃圾桶，接着另一名職員手拿篩子，撈走大鐵桶內漂浮在「口水油」表面的雜物。<br />\n<br />\n及後大鐵桶內的「口水油」靜置過濾後，職員便再次裝到火鍋盆內翻熱，再撒上乾辣椒及香料後，由侍應捧到顧客的餐桌。報道指，有顧客曾向職員查詢湯底問題，對方明確回應稱店方所使用的是「一次性鍋底」。<br />\n<br />\n報道還指，火鍋店翻用顧客食用過的火鍋油，如坑渠油一樣同屬回收的「口水油」，而這樣的「口水油」經反覆加熱、循環使用，會產生大量對人體有害的物質，早已被明令禁止使用。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，大隊長主題火鍋是重慶火鍋排名前十強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而在2017年12月，重慶市火鍋協會聯合商委、食藥監局等部門認定全市第一批「放心火鍋店」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，大隊長主題火鍋北城天街店也名列其中。"},{"pid":"95b528567383bf95d9a46ca0599e0ce1093d7256","tid":525932,"uid":30169,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"你老味"},{"pid":"1176ff939757aecd07305ba4bce3eed9f72df173","tid":525932,"uid":64009,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"放低良心"},{"pid":"4f7a1a71b8dac54b4dbec87353cbe8983cf8f859","tid":525932,"uid":34223,"like":184,"dislike":2,"score":182,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"中國係環保方面真係好有成就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285f64b7aad55f5206c000558c541438635ddcc4","tid":525932,"uid":90704,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"呢啲先夠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92acf46d9e1538c1d0b8a6bc57c952d7e5f8d52","tid":525932,"uid":30169,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"有個post 話乜撚嘢大陸食嘢好香港九倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57772b4957ef912d588c5655da115b581aed5ab5","tid":525932,"uid":48973,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:47:28.000Z","msg":"過濾過已經好好"},{"pid":"650ff77e95c9144079f30408593d4b9db2fae59d","tid":525932,"uid":75326,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"1176ff939757aecd07305ba4bce3eed9f72df173","tid":525932,"uid":64009,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"放低良心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"萬兩黃金"},{"pid":"e57928421557bbf91ee5e2ff6839fa12db95c974","tid":525932,"uid":136735,"like":82,"dislike":4,"score":78,"quote":{"pid":"a92acf46d9e1538c1d0b8a6bc57c952d7e5f8d52","tid":525932,"uid":30169,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T07:46:52.000Z","msg":"有個post 話乜撚嘢大陸食嘢好香港九倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"